parameters: \C[23][Luna]\C[0] "The time has finally come. I've been waiting for this day."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I'm not here to defeat who you were then. I'm here to defeat
who you are now."
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "Pfft... Hahaha... What's that supposed to mean?"
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I'm here to defeat what you've become."

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "That time? What you've become? I've forgotten all about the
past."
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "So? Do you have some sort of plan to win?"
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I have something left behind by Regnus Grahardt."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "(Regnus Grahardt... I'm going to open the magic box.)"

.The party's level has increased by '3'..All health has been fully
restored
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "Ancient magic? Forbidden magic? No, something else...?"

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "(This is quite advanced magic. Even I am seeing it for the
first time...)"
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "(Regnus Grahardt... It seems he does exist.)"
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "(Where is he... If he exists, why doesn't he show himself?)"

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I know you're not at full strength yet... Show me the power of
your lineage."
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "It seems I have no choice but to show you."

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "I'll put you to sleep with the power of my lineage for the
last time."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I know you're not at full strength yet... Show me the power of
your lineage."
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "There's no need to show it, is there?"

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "Well, fine. I'll put you to sleep with the power of my direct
lineage for the last time."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "While I was on an expedition to another country, Lady Reysia
was killed. You killed your own mother, Lady Reysia, to obtain that
direct-line power."

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "That's right. She seemed like she would live a long time, so I
killed her while she was sleeping. Hehe."

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "Who cares about such a person, as long as I could inherit the
power."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Everyone, from here on, I will fight alone."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I probably won't win. That's why I want you to escape from
this castle."
\C[24][Cain]\C[0] "I'm going home. I can't keep up with this anymore."
Kyle: "It's reckless. We're already struggling even with everyone."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I intended to do this from the start. I thought it would come
to this."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I should be the only one to die."

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] "When it's time to die, we said we'd always be together, didn't
we...? Luuna..."
\C[24][Cain]\C[0] "Becky, let's go! Luuna is prepared to die."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Kyle-san, please take care of Becky and Cain."

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "Only one needs to die? Well, of course. It seems you've run
out of options?"

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "It's fine by me, I have no intention of chasing after them.
Once you're dead, everything else will fall into place."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Do you think I've given up on the fight?"

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Do you really think I came here without any chance of winning,
driven only by emotion?"

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Direct descendants of sorcerers are neither invincible nor
immortal. You, who killed my mother, should know that best, shouldn't
you?
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] What are you trying to say?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Indeed, you are a sorcerer of the direct lineage, extraordinary
beyond measure.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] But do you think I, who have been watching from afar, haven't
done anything?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] It's true that direct descendants of sorcerers possess
unimaginable magical power.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] However, due to your overconfidence and arrogance, you will
lose to me.

Sylvia: Lucia! What does this mean!? Luuna's personality is that of a
sore loser!?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Sylvia, I'll explain what that means right now.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The azure magic that places limits on one's own sorcery...
"Chain Binds Magic"
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The reason I became a member of the resistance...

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The first reason is that you allied with the magical superpower
of Valentina and betrayed the people of this country...

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The second reason is that I cannot tolerate sorcerers who
surpass me, especially cruel black witches like you.
Sylvia: She's not just an ordinary pacifist resistance member...?

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Hehe... Luuna, I had forgotten about that aspect of your
personality.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] You always looked at me with those eyes while keeping a cool
face.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] It was Luuna who let our comrades return, was it because you
didn't want your true feelings to be heard?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Those people are a nuisance. With a false self, I lack
concentration and can't unleash my true power.
Sylvia: Lucia, what do you mean? Was Luuna pretending all along?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I always thought I would surpass you one day.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Hehe... That's so like you. You've been training with self-
imposed handicaps.
Sylvia: During the battle at the fortress, was Luuna holding back?
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] That seems to be the case.
Sylvia: Is Luuna saying she's a sorcerer on par with me and Lucia?

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] She may not have the innate talents that I or my sister-in-law
possess, but she is a hard worker enough to make up for it. A futile
effort though. Hehe...

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] At first, I joined the resistance to enhance my own abilities.
But now it's different. It's not just for myself anymore.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Chain Binds Magic", now is the time to release these chains.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Here I go. You will realize the extent of my true power.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] For torturing and killing Mao and Mei, I will never forgive
you!

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I will never forgive you for torturing and killing those
children!
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I will never forgive you! Here I come!
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I'll make it easy for you.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Uaaaaaaaah---!! (Mao, Mei, Becky, everyone, Lady Ceres, Rinny,
Luca, Regnus Grahardt... This is the final battle! Lend me your
strength...!)
Sylvia: Luuna is pushing forward... Could it be... even Lucia is...
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I will seal that power again.
Sylvia: I don't care about the match anymore!
Sylvia: Lucia! Hilda! We're going to crush this one together!
Sylvia: Hilda! Increase your magical power more!
Sylvia: The match is already over!
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I'm sorry, Luuna. The match is over.
